## REMEMBER

1. **SEMANTIC tokens only** (`--uds-color-*`, `--uds-space-*`, `--uds-font-*`). NEVER `--uds-primitive-*`.
2. **NEVER hardcode** colors, spacing, or fonts. Always `var(--uds-*)`.
3. **The HTML in this rule is example shape, not production framework code**. For React/Vue/etc., use the framework-agnostic web components from the UDS Storybook.
